# Logical Ontology Definitions (experimental, private or proprietary)

@prefix raci: <https://symbol.systems/v0/onto/raci#>.
@prefix fact: <https://symbol.systems/v0/onto/fact#>.
@prefix frames: <https://symbol.systems/v0/onto/frames#>.
